        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>When you pull up the hood of this nondescript gray cloak (an Interact action), you become drab and uninteresting, gaining a +2 item bonus to Stealth checks and to Deception checks to Impersonate a forgettable background character, such as a servant, but also taking a -1 item penalty to Diplomacy and Intimidation checks.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.equipment-effects.Effect: Clandestine Cloak (Greater)]{Effect: Clandestine Cloak (Greater)}</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span> envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You pull the cloak's hood up and gain the benefits of a 5th-level @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Nondetection]{Nondetection} for 8 hours or until you pull the hood back down, whichever comes first.</p>"
